Dear <%= @santa.name %>

Your on the list for <%= @list.name %>!

You are a Secret Santa for <%= @recipient.name %>.

Remember to keep it a secret!

Note: Your organiser, <%= @list.user.given_names %>, has set the day to exchange gifts to be on <%= @list.gift_day.strftime("%A, %B %-d, %Y") %>.

<% if @list.gift_value.present? && @list.gift_value > 0 %>
  <p>Please note that the gift value set by #{@list.user.given_names} is: $#{@list.gift_value}</p>
<% end %>

Thanks for participating, and have a great day!

Captain Santa
